Dialogs.Dialog: I'm glad... You came here for me.
Sorry for suddenly calling you out...
I don't mind. What do you about？
Today, I have something to give you, Sempai...
My gaze as I look upon me...
Our glances overlap. Ah... It is a spiral maze.
Will you rescue me from labyrinth？
Or will my heart be locked away by your chain of love？
It doesn't matter which one. Either way, your magical eyes eternity...
T-That's not it！ Oh no！ How could I be so careless...？
This is the real one！ Please read this one！
The sky is so blue, but my heart is cloudy.
Intentionally taking 10 fast steps, I walked past him pretending to look indifferent.
The feeling is like when you look at the bus that you have missed. It's the loneliness.
For this letter... Please pretend this didn't happen！
Because this should really... I think this is something that should be said in person.
So, I'm changing my strategy！ Today I am... Um... Now, I panic...
In a little while, after I arrange my thoughts, will you listen to what I have to say？
Well then, thank you very much！
Ah... I haven't introduced myself yet, have I？
Anegasaki Nene, 14 years old, eighth grader. Currently in unrequited love！
How nice~！ It felt like a real confession...
Now！ Catch me if you can~！！ Hehehe！
(Oh...！ It's my chance. All right, I'll soak her！)
Geez！ I said "No"！ I'm soaking wet！
Not yet, not yet~！ Take~ this~！
Aaaah~ Geez~！ Look. I'm all wet now！
Ah... Sorry, sorry！ Maybe I went too far.
I have to dry my shirt... Wait a minute.
Actually, this is the real thing...
Huh！？ What？ It was a dream...？
(Alright, let's sprinkle water on shirt as a tease！)
Sensei？ ...Why are you here？ And... how did I become this small！？
Geez, what's wrong？ Are you feeling sick？
Then let's start the game, okay？
...I don't think I can do that...
You must do it properly. Okay, put your hands on your head... Pompoko-rin~
(When I was a kid, did I enjoy doing something like this？)
That was great. The next one is Pompoko-jump.
First, you sit like this, and swing your tail~
Swing your tail~ Eh？ Sensei, that thing on your back...
Okay, once more. Swing your tail~
A tail！ That's a raccoon dog's tail！！
Yeah？ You also have it, right？
Eh？ ...Ah！ I also have a tail！？
Hehe. We're raccoon dogs. Everyone has a tail.
I-I didn't know that. So, I'm a raccoon dog...？
I'm a raccoon dog. You're a raccoon dog. Everyone's a raccoon dog. Pompoko-rin♪
O-Okay. Yeah, I'm also a raccoon dog...
Okay, now for the last time... Pompoko-beam~！
Right, it must have been a dream.
Why did I see that dream？ And why a raccoon dog...？
But if I could have ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ as my day-care sensei, that'd be nice.
A new sensei is coming today. I wonder how this new sensei will be.
If we get a pretty sensei, that'd be nice...
(A sexy sensei like her isn't bad at all...)
Look at me. Just look at me... Okay？
(Heart or raccoon dog？ I think I'll go with heart.)
(I just have to repeat after her, huh...？)
Hey！ That's too soon for you, you know...？
That's it for our class today. See you later！
Sensei！ Hit me with that raccoon dog, please！
I can't possibly tell ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ about this dream...
(I'd better stop now or she'll keep hitting me with that whip...)
(The sensei, did you say “I love you”...)
Say to the microphone “I love you”
Say to the microphone “I need you”
Say to the microphone “I want you”
Amazing... I wonder who built it.
That voice... Could that be ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
You idiot！ I'm the king here！
What...？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！？ You're so tiny and so cute...
You got a problem with me！？
No, not at all. By the way, where is this？
This？ This is my secret base！
You must be a secret agenda！
You sneaked into my secret base to steal my information, right！？
S-Shut up！ Well, I think you can say it that way...
Anyway！ If you're not the secret agenda, then say your vow！
Everyone in my kingdom knows it！
You~！ You must really be a secret agenda！
Shut up！ I'm going to beat you black and blue and cut you into pieces~！
Oh no！ I have to escape！
Phew... She almost beat me black and blue and cut me into pieces...
That little ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was such a mischievous kid.
Now, you can be my servant！
Haha！ It's my honor. Thank you very much.
Now, hurry up. You have your duty！
Well... Go to buy 3 onions, 3 potatoes, 2 carrots... And 250 grams or beef...
Anyway！ Just take this memo and buy everything listed in it！
You want me to... go shopping for you？
Right！ If it's my duty, you do it for me！
Oh no...！ The enemy is attacking！
Hey, Nene！ You're still there！？ I told you to go shopping for me！
For that... I'm getting my servant to buy it now... Right？ Right！？
You're doing this again！？ Enough. Go home now！
I'm really sorry. This girl's always acting like a boy. Hey, go home！
That ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was such a mischievous kid.
By the way... From the ingredients, was her mom going to make curry？
Geez... This is the hot spring. We secretly came here.
Hehe. You must still be half asleep. Look. It's already dark. ...The moon is very pretty tonight...
Having a peaceful vacation like this is nice, huh...？
(The best thing is... to see ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s face when the moonlight is shining on her. She is so pretty...)
Hah... The wind feels good... Especially after getting out of the hot bath, you know？
(...I can smell ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s soap from the wind...)
Ah, the wind really feels good.
I got into the hot spring again after you fell asleep. I was in there 3 times already. Now, I'm feeling dizzy. Hehe.
You should go there after this, okay？ I think you were sweating while you slept.
Ah, right. How about we take a walk outside after you get out of the bath？ It's not bad to walk under the moonlight, right？
(Today, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ looks very mature... I can't believe she's really my girlfriend...)
Hehe. I had dreamed of a trip with just the two of us before and now it came true. Let's go somewhere together again, okay...？
(...Am I an appropriate man for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Somehow, I'm starting to worry...)
What's wrong？ You suddenly spaced out. Hehe. Are you still sleepy？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, why are you dating someone like me？
Why...？ You asked me？ Of course, it's because...
Okay... But... Why do you love me？
...cool, kind, and cute. But you're also very reliable. Moreover, you treasure me. Also, you...
W-Wait, wait. I'm asking you seriously...
Ah, a dream...？ If that's really what she thinks about me, that'd be great...
(The wind after taking a bath feels good...)
I ate a lot today. I'm full...
Hey, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！ What are you doing here in the middle of the night？
Lately, there have been horrible incidents going on around here. It's dangerous.
Okay...？ I don't think it's okay at all.
And you look so pale. Are you sick？
Anyway, it's dangerous for you to be alone. I'll walk you home.
What are you saying！？ How can I forget about you！？
Because... I don't want to see you anymore...
Don't be ridiculous！ I'll walk you home. Come on！
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... I'd better look at her carefully.)
I'm such a disgrace... So, please leave me alone...
The incident was that a vampire was attacking people... Don't tell me it was you, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！
Stop it... Don't look at me like that！
Even the sun has abandoned me... You, too... You should just forget about me.
Don't speak nonsense！ How can I abandon my beloved ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！？
I'll always remember your words even when I have to live my life alone in the darkness, for eternity...
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... I can't leave you alone...)
Make me a vampire, too！ Then we both can live together for eternity！
I can't... I absolutely can't do that！
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I don't mind that as long as I can be with you. So, go ahead and suck my blood.
Really？ Now then, I'll do as you wish！ Actually, I'm pretty hungry~
Eh！？ Are you doing this for real...？ Well, um...
U-Um... What did you eat today？
What...？ I only ate some dumplings.
Phew... I'm safe... Eh？ It was a dream？
...I didn't really abandon her, did I？
(That？ What about the wound on your neck？)
(Exhale and calm down before you can eat...)
Touch the wound at the neck
Okay, you'd like the pancakes and drink set, right？ Please wait a moment~
Geez... Don't ask me that question. We're in the middle of work, so you'd better pay full attention.
Hehe. Okay, for a sleepyhead like you, can you clean up table 3 for me？
Thank you for waiting. Have you decided what you'd like to order？
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s current uniform is a bit tighter than her usual one...)
Thank you very much. Please visit us again. We'll be waiting.
You can take a break after the lunch hour, so just keep it up, okay？ Hehehe.
Okay... Ah, customers at table 5 are calling you.
Kyaa. No... What should I do...？ It seems to be broken...
Let me take a look... Yeah, you're right. I don't think you can close it.
That can't be true. I think this uniform is just smaller than your usual one.
But I also just changed my school uniform to a bigger size. I'm getting bigger than when I entered high school.
No, it's not because you're getting fat, but it's because you're growing taller. You're still a young girl.
Of course. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ isn't fat at all.
Thanks... I don't know what I'd do if you thought I was fat...
Did you mean it when you said I'm still a young girl？
Thanks！ Now, I'm going back to work.
Wait, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！ Your zipper is going to break apart！
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was cute when she flustered...
Why are you making that face？
Graduation... But it's not time for ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s graduation yet...
No. I've already graduated. Look at the cherry blossoms...
Huh？ Ah, you're right. I see... So it's time for the graduation already.
Yeah. And from now on, I'm done with you.
Yeah, congrat-- Eh？ What did you just say？ You're done with what...？
From now on, I'm done with you.
It's sad... But I've already graduated and I have to leave.
What？ Why is it so sudden！？
Because you don't need me anymore.
That's not true！ That's absolutely not true！！
You're lying. You didn't come to see me at all.
Never mind... It's fine now. I already understand.
...Eh？ Was that... a dream？ What a relief...
...Where am I？ Huh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ What's the matter？
...Hmm, seems like I got a cold... *cough* *cough* Thank you for coming here to visit me today.
A cold？ How do you feel now？
Well, I think I'm getting a little better...
Really？ Then do you still have a fever...？
I see... Right. You should eat something, okay？ Is there anything you want to eat？
I lost my appetite... But... Ah.
I want to eat some grated apple...
Grated apple？ Got it. Can I use your kitchen？
...Hehe. I'll let you spoil me for today...
Okay, just wait a little bit.
What is it？ Just tell me what you want.
I still can't get up... Can you feed me？
Well... You can't eat by yourself？
...I just want you to feed me... You can't？
O-Of course I can！ ...Then open your mouth. Okay.
Hmph. That's not my mouth... Don't tease me.
Hmm... Hehe, yummy. Hey, I want more... Now, ahhhhh~
(Is it because she is sick and weak that ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is acting like a kid now？ She's cute.)
You don't have to praise me so much.
...Delicious. Thanks so much. Somehow, I think I'm getting much better.
That's good. If you have an appetite now, you'll recover soon.
I want to stay sick like this a little longer...
When ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ was acting like a spoiled child, she was so cute...
